\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6454914 From Fr Seraphim Holland PO 37 McKinney TX 75070}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6454914\charrsid13641497 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497\charrsid13641497 Dear }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5513235 ...}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497\charrsid13641497 :}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10909999  T}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497 hank you for your letter. My hope is to visit}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5513235  you....}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497 
\par 
\par You can easily make a
 new start with a clean state. Finishing is a little harder, but if you are serious, and pray, and make intelligent choices, you will prosper. I pray for you daily now, and you must learn to pray. If you depend on God in all things, not just in your mind,
 but viscerally in your entire being, you will have success. I want to learn about how you pray and how much. You should confess as regularly as possibly Reading the Gospels }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247 daily}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497  is essential, and the Psalter too. We will talk about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247 all these things as soon as possible.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13641497 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247 
\par I will give you some advice. Make }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\insrsid792247\charrsid10909999 sure your prayer is not hindered.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10909999 T}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247 he greatest specific hindrances to prayer are remembering wrongs, judging others, pride, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10909999 hurting others }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247 
and sexual sin. The way to attack all these things is with prayer and fasting. 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10909999 Y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid792247 
ou are divorced. If you have any ill feelings towards your ex wife, whether they are deserved or not, you must pray for her every day. Being in prison creates enemies and some friends, and you must pray for both, your enemies and those who h
ave hurt you, or tried to hurt you, every day. It is simple to pray for others. 
\par 
